+## 1. Vision reconstruction — what Boss is trying to build
+
+Boss is not trying to build “German lessons in an app.”
+
+He is trying to build a premium, Kerala-rooted Goethe A1 course for Malayali beginners who want Germany but start from zero, with exam pressure, family/job/visa stakes, and low patience for textbook boredom.
+
+Plain version:
+
+Adipoli German should feel like a guided Kerala-to-Germany A1 coach. The learner opens the app, enters a tiny situation, hears real German, replies aloud or writes something useful, repairs one likely beginner mistake, and leaves with a named ability that helps in Goethe A1 and real life.
